item.title: Hurlers Retain Title (Almost)
item.author: Mitchell Cuddihy,
item.description: Much like Leonidas and his 300 Spartans, Sat 3rd November found me leading 10 Imperial hurlers. This time however the hammer would fall, not in Thermopylae, but in Birmingham. Same difference some would say. The challenge facing us was very much as daunting. Our titanic adversaries were University â€¦
